    srs-kg:pinyin "Nǐ zhīdao zhèlǐ de dōngtiān duō lěng ma?" ;
    srs-kg:translationEN "Do you know how cold it is here in winter?"@en .

srs-inst:sent-gp-a2-072-asking-about-degree-with-duo-010 a srs-kg:Sentence ;
