    srs-kg:pinyin "Wǒ hé nǐ yīyàng." ;
    srs-kg:translationEN "I am the same as you."@en .

srs-inst:sent-gp-a2-073-basic-comparisons-with-yiyang-002 a srs-kg:Sentence ;
