    srs-kg:pinyin "Měiguó wénhuà gēn Zhōngguó wénhuà bù yīyàng." ;
    srs-kg:translationEN "America culture and Chinese culture are not alike."@en .

srs-inst:sent-gp-a2-073-basic-comparisons-with-yiyang-006 a srs-kg:Sentence ;
