    srs-kg:pinyin "Píjiǔ hé pútaojiǔ de wèidao yīyàng ma?" ;
    srs-kg:translationEN "Do beer and red wine taste the same?"@en .

srs-inst:sent-gp-a2-073-basic-comparisons-with-yiyang-007 a srs-kg:Sentence ;
