    srs-kg:pinyin "Tā hé tā gēge yīyàng gāo." ;
    srs-kg:translationEN "She and her older brother are equally tall."@en .

srs-inst:sent-gp-a2-073-basic-comparisons-with-yiyang-009 a srs-kg:Sentence ;
